    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7780_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>Enclosed Invoices of <hi rend="underline">8 Cases</hi> <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>of Goods containing parts of the
        <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>Boring Machine Working Tools –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7780_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>The Cases are numbered as follows
        <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/><choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice><hi rend="underline">4</hi>, <hi rend="underline">7</hi>, <hi rend="underline">8</hi>, <hi rend="underline">9</hi>, <hi rend="underline">10</hi>, <hi rend="underline">11</hi>, <hi rend="underline">12</hi>, + <hi rend="underline">13</hi> making
        <lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>a total of 13 Cases sent by me,
        <lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>trusting All will arrive safe
        <lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>such completes all I have to
        <lb xml:id="p1-l25"/>send –</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
